  <div>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_bronchoscopy">Bronchoscopy</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_clinical_investigation">Clinical Investigation</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_bronchoscopy">Bronchoscopy</xref>
 is a procedure that allows a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 to take 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_cell">CELLS</xref>
 from the inside of the lungs.        </p>
    <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_bronchoscopy">Bronchoscopies</xref>, see the NHS website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/lung-cancer/diagnosis/" scope="external" format="html">Bronchoscopy and biopsy</xref>.        </p>
